hp.description: The OMEN Laptop is ready to go wherever you are. Enjoy desktop-level power with a 12th Gen Intel® Core™ processor[1] and a modern graphics card, both regulated by OMEN Tempest Cooling. The screen is equally impressive with high resolution and TUV Eyesafe Low Blue Light [2]. This gaming laptop even lets you expand with plenty of USB ports[3,4].
